ORDER CONFIRMATION - <%= @fundraiser.name %>
============================================

Thank you for your order!

Hi <%= @order.customer_name || 'there' %>,

Thank you for supporting <%= @fundraiser.organization_name %> through this fundraiser. Your order has been received and is being processed.

ORDER DETAILS
-------------
Order Number: #<%= @order.order_number %>
Order Date: <%= @order.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
<% if @participant %>Supporting: <%= @participant.name %><% end %>

ORDER SUMMARY
-------------
<% @order.fundraiser_order_items.each do |item| %>
- <%= item.product_name %><% if item.variant_name.present? %> (<%= item.variant_name %>)<% end %>
  Qty: <%= item.quantity %> | Price: $<%= '%.2f' % (item.total_price_cents / 100.0) %>
<% end %>

Subtotal: $<%= '%.2f' % (@order.subtotal_cents / 100.0) %>
<% if @order.shipping_cents.to_i > 0 %>Shipping: $<%= '%.2f' % (@order.shipping_cents / 100.0) %><% end %>
<% if @order.tax_cents.to_i > 0 %>Tax: $<%= '%.2f' % (@order.tax_cents / 100.0) %><% end %>
TOTAL: $<%= '%.2f' % (@order.total_cents / 100.0) %>

<% if @order.has_shipping_address? %>
SHIPPING TO
-----------
<%= @order.full_shipping_address %>
<% elsif @fundraiser.pickup_location.present? %>
PICKUP INFORMATION
------------------
<%= @fundraiser.pickup_location %>
<% if @fundraiser.pickup_instructions.present? %>
<%= @fundraiser.pickup_instructions %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

QUESTIONS?
----------
If you have any questions about your order, please contact:
<% if @fundraiser.contact_name.present? %><%= @fundraiser.contact_name %><% end %>
<% if @fundraiser.contact_email.present? %><%= @fundraiser.contact_email %><% end %>
<% if @fundraiser.contact_phone.present? %><%= @fundraiser.contact_phone %><% end %>

Thank you for your support!

